quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  59,11,"Mbela a yi*aani Й“een naafaqinЙ“e wiiЙ“e musibbe mum en yedduЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e defte, si on yaltii pellet ma min yaltid e mon, min Й—ototaako e dow mon hay gooto, si on kaЙ“aama ma min mballu mon Alla na seedo koЙ“e fenooЙ“e"
  59,12,SiЙ“e yaltinaama Й“e yaltidtah e mum en si Й“e kaЙ“aama Й“e wallataa Й“e siЙ“e walliiЙ“e maЙ“e runta refti Й“e walletaake
  59,13,"Ko onon Й“uri sattu kulo e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e gaa nih e Alla, waЙ—i noon koЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“e paamatah"
  59,14,Й“e haЙ“atah e mon si wonah hoЙ“e e gure taartinaaЙ—e galli wolla caggal mahdeele bone maЙ“Й“e hakkunde mum en na satti haЙ—a sikka koЙ“e gootum kono Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e na ceerti waЙ—i noon koЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“e kakkiltah
  59,15,Hona yeru Й“een adiiЙ“e Й“e ko Й“adii Й“e meeЙ—i lepte fiyaaku mum en woodaniiЙ“e lepte cattuЙ—e
  59,16,"Ko hono seytaane nde wi*i neЙ—Й—anke o yeddu, nde o yeddi o wi*i miin komi kisЙ—o e ma, miin mbeЙ—o huli Alla jom binnde O"
  59,17,"Laati batte mum en kanЙ“e Й—iЙ—a ko yiite saasooЙ“e toon, Й—uum ko njoЙ“di tooГұooЙ“e"
  59,18,"Eehey mon goonЙ—ibe ndeente Alla, yo fittaandu ndaar kondu ardinani jannga kule Alla pellet Alla ko kumpatiiЙ—o ko ngolloton ko"
  59,19,"Wote ngone hono Й“een yejjitЙ“e Alla, O yejjitini Й“e pittaali mum en ko Й“een ngoni faasiqeeЙ“e"
  59,20,"YimЙ“e yiite e yimЙ“e aljanna potatah, ko yimЙ“e aljanna ngoni foolЙ“e"
  59,21,Si min tellinna o quraana e dow hooseere ma a yiinde honde huli honde fetta ngam hulde Alla Й—i tinndi emin piyaniЙ—i yimЙ“e ko ngam Й“e miijo
  59,22,"Ko kanko woni deweteeЙ—o deweteeЙ—o e goonga alah si wonah kanko, ganndo ko wirni e ka wirnaaki kank woni jom yurmeende huftadinnde e yurmeende heeriinde"
  59,23,Ko kanko Alla mbo deweteeЙ—o e goonga alah si wonah kanko laamЙ—o ceniiЙ—o kisЙ—o goonЙ—iЙ—o kiilndiiЙ—o tedduЙ—o cemmbinЙ—o mawЙ—o senaare woodanii Alla e koЙ“e ndenndinta mbo ko
  59,24,"Ko kanko woni Alla tagЙ—o gootnuЙ—o mbaadinЙ—o tagu woodanii mbo inЙ—e Й“urЙ—e moЖҙЖҙude, woodanii mbo ko woni e nder kammuuji e leydi ko kanko woni pooloowo mbo hay gooto foolatah Г‘eeГұЖҙuЙ—o"
  60,1,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e wote njaggire aГұЙ“e Mi e aГұЙ“e mon heetЙ“e hoЙ—on mberlo e mum en gilli te koЙ“e yedduЙ“e goongo garЙ—o o e mon, hoЙ“e njaltina nelaaЙ—o e onon sabu tan on ngoonЙ—anii Alla joomi mon, tawde on njalti sabu jihaadi e laawol Am e Й—aЙ“jude weluya am, hoЙ—on cuurtanaЙ“e kabaruuji juulЙ“e ngam Й“e mbele mon, MbeЙ—a anndi ko cuuЙ—oton e ko Й“anngiЙ—on, kala e mon baЙ—Й—o Й—uum o majji laawol peewngol"
  60,2,SiЙ“e peewnatiima e mon Й“e ngOnana mon aГұЙ“e Й“e mberta juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e Й—emЙ—e mum en e mbaadi mbonndi Й“e njiЙ—iina nde ngonaton heefereeЙ“e
  60,3,Nafatah on enЙ—ameeje mon wonah Й“iЙ“Й“e mon Гұande darnga O seernda hakkunde mon Alla na yi*a ko golloton ko
  60,4,"Woodanii on Гұeemtinirde moЖҙЖҙere e Ibraahiima e Й“een wonduЙ“e e mum nde Й“e mbi*i pellet ko min hisЙ“e e mon e ko ndewaton ko wonah Alla ko, min njeddii on feeГұi hakkunde men ngaГұngu e tikkere haa pooma haa ngoonЙ—inon Alla gooto O, si wonah konngol Ibraahiima wonande baaba makko pellet ma mi yaafnano ma, mi alanaama hay huunde ka Alla, joomi amen min mbakkaliima e Ma ko e Ma min ndutti e ko e Ma woni wattande"
  60,5,"joomi amen wota waЙ— min fitina wonande Й“een yedduЙ“e, yaafa amen joomi amen pellet ko aan woni tedduЙ—o mbo fooletaake ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o"
  60,6,"Woodaniina mon e maЙ“Й“e Гұeemtanirgal moЖҙЖҙal wonande oon joortiiЙ—o e Alla e Гұalngu laakara, oon Й—uurniiЙ—o noon Pellet Alla ko gala jettaaЙ—o"